{"submission_id":"sub_b97afe55dfaaa68b","run_id":"2026-06-21T23-25-12-330Z_3137823-ef4726aa_ingest_meeting-doc-43906","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T23:35:19.256Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:b97afe55dfaaa68b161671100402152147d7e093ef2a4f91167c653e76f80447","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_43906","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_43906_total_ytd_driver","label":"Total Overtime YTD Variance Driver","raw_text":"YTD June costs were $3M below Budget. Major drivers of the unfavorable non-reimbursable YTD variance include higher vacancy/absentee coverage requirements and higher-than-expected weather-related events at NYCT, partially offset by lower maintenance requirements, and reduced traffic congestion/lower unscheduled service at MTA Bus; lower requirements for maintenance, and tightened management procedures at the LIRR; revised T&E crew requirements at MNR; revised MTAPD deployment assumptions at MTA HQ; and managerial efficiencies and rescheduled maintenance at B&T.","payload":{"claim_text":"YTD June costs were $3M below Budget. Major drivers of the unfavorable non-reimbursable YTD variance include higher vacancy/absentee coverage requirements and higher-than-expected weather-related events at NYCT, partially offset by lower maintenance requirements, and reduced traffic congestion/lower unscheduled service at MTA Bus; lower requirements for maintenance, and tightened management procedures at the LIRR; revised T&E crew requirements at MNR; revised MTAPD deployment assumptions at MTA HQ; and managerial efficiencies and rescheduled maintenance at B&T.","data_type":"variance_driver","data_type_normalized":{"raw_text":"variance_driver","normalized_value":"variance_driver"}},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_43906","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_43906#p003_c0007","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_43906/blocks.jsonl","page_number":3,"block_id":"p003_c0007","text_sha256":"sha256:3f14866ce112a39faf1d030a64d266533fc39da4ea28